data.description: Welcome to this private Stallion Meadows 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home nestled at the end of the road, where a harmonious blend of comfort and functionality awaits. This home features OWNED Solar PLUS a TESLA Power Wall with newer attached garage. The heart of the home is the expansive living room, adorned with wet bar and fireplace that provide both functionality and aesthetic appeal. The focal point of this inviting space is the brick wood-burning fireplace, which exudes warmth and charm creating the perfect ambiance for cozy evenings with loved ones. Prepare to be impressed by the spacious kitchen with ample storage space, every gadget and utensil finds its rightful place, maintaining an organized and clutter-free environment. The kitchen showcases newer stainless steel appliances that effortlessly combine style and functionality. The granite countertops not only elevate the aesthetic appeal but also offer a durable and easy-to-maintain workspace for your culinary adventures. Escape to the large master suite, a private retreat that boasts its own en-suite bathroom and his and hers closets. This personal haven provides both comfort and convenience, offering a tranquil space to unwind and rejuvenate after a long day. The two additional bedrooms are versatile spaces that can cater to your family's needs. Whether you're accommodating a growing family, welcoming guests, or setting up a home office, these rooms offer endless possibilities. Step outside to discover the gorgeous view, and back patio for gatherings. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this beautiful house your forever home. Schedule a viewing today and prepare to fall in love with the endless possibilities and comfort this home has to offer!
